---
title: Decision Record Template
---

# Decision Record Template

::summary
Capture the decision, why it matters now, and the date or event that should trigger review.
::

::decision{id="decision" status="proposed" owner="team"}
We propose option B because it best balances user value, implementation cost, and reversibility.
::

::grid{columns=3}
:::card{title="Option A"}
Describe the safest or simplest option.
:::

:::card{title="Option B"}
Describe the recommended option.
:::

:::card{title="Option C"}
Describe the high-upside or high-risk option.
:::
::

::risk{id="decision-risk" owner="team" severity="medium"}
Name the primary risk and the mitigation plan.
::

::agent_task{id="decision-review" scope="post-launch"}
After the first milestone, check whether the decision criteria still hold and add a `::state_change` block if they changed.
::
